class vizasm.model.objc.AsmParserInterface.AsmParserInterface[source]¶

Interface for creating an object from a line of assembler code.

Methods

create_from_asm_line(asmline, cpu) Parse a line of asm code and try to create an instance of the object from which the method has been called.
static create_from_asm_line(asmline, cpu)[source]¶

Parse a line of asm code and try to create an instance of the object from which the method has been called. Return None if not possible.

Parameters:

asmline: string :

cpu: Cpu :

the cpu/architecture to use
